{
  "formatter": {
    "kind": "jwt-auth",
    "type": "super-auth",
    "useAuthz": "&useAuthz",
    "failureAuthAllow": "&failureAuthAllow",
    "cacheSwitch": "&cacheSwitch",
    "authz_result_cache": "&authz_result_cache"
  },
  "layouts": [
    {
      "key": "useAuthz",
      "alias": "鉴权",
      "help": "开关关闭后，则只会对客户端请求进行认证，所有合法的外部认证都可以访问；开关打开后，会在认证成功后判断对应的外部认证是否被成功授权",
      "type": "switch",
      "default": false
    },
    {
      "key": "failureAuthAllow",
      "alias": "允许匿名访问",
      "help": "仅对无需鉴权的情况可配置，开启允许匿名访问后，即使认证失败也会将请求继续转发到后端服务，只是转发后相关的认证请求头为空",
      "type": "switch",
      "default": false,
      "visible": {
        "this.useAuthz": false
      }
    },
    {
      "key": "cacheSwitch",
      "alias": "是否认证缓存",
      "type": "switch"
    },
    {
      "key": "authz_result_cache",
      "alias": "认证缓存配置",
      "type": "layouts",
      "help": "配置认证缓存相关信息，包括缓存key以及缓存ttl",
      "visible": {
        "true": [
          "this",
          "cacheSwitch"
        ]
      },
      "layouts": [
        {
          "key": "result_cache_key",
          "alias": "缓存key配置",
          "help": "配置缓存key，默认情况，JWT认证和Oauth2认证采用header:authority,签名认证采用header：x-nsf-accesskey作为缓存key",
          "type": "layouts",
          "layouts":[
            {
              "key": "ignore_case",
              "alias": "key忽略大小写",
              "type": "switch",
              "default": true
            },
            {
              "key": "headers_keys",
              "alias": "自定义请求头",
              "help": "可选配置，如果不配置则采用默认配置",
              "type": "multi_input"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "key": "result_cache_ttl",
          "alias": "缓存ttl配置",
          "help": "指定缓存时间，单位ms",
          "type": "input",
          "rules": [
            "Required",
            "Number",
            "MinNumber(0)",
            "MaxNumber(99999999)"
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}